"```sql\nSELECT AVG(\n    CAST(SUBSTR(results.fastestLapTime, 1, INSTR(results.fastestLapTime, ':') - 1) AS INTEGER) * 60 +\n    CAST(SUBSTR(results.fastestLapTime, INSTR(results.fastestLapTime, ':') + 1) AS REAL)\n) AS average_fastest_lap_time_seconds\nFROM drivers\nINNER JOIN results ON drivers.driverId = results.driverId\nWHERE drivers.forename = 'Lewis' AND drivers.surname = 'Hamilton';\n```"